## Core Features

### Dashboard Overview
- **Portfolio Summary:**
  - Current BTC Holdings
  - Portfolio Value (USD)
  - Cost Basis
  - Unrealized Gains/Losses
  - ROI Percentage

- **Performance Charts:**
  - Portfolio Value Over Time
  - Cost Basis Line
  - BTC Price Overlay
  - Time Range Filters (1M, 3M, 6M, 1Y, All)

- **Market Indicators:**
  - Bitcoin Current Price
  - 24h Change
  - Fear & Greed Index

### Performance Analytics
- **KPI Tiles:**
  - ROI (Return on Investment)
  - 30-Day Performance
  - YTD (Year-to-Date) Performance
  - All-Time High Portfolio Value

- **Performance Chart:**
  - Interactive line chart with date range selection
  - Toggle between portfolio value and cost basis
  - Benchmark against Bitcoin price

- **Advanced Metrics:**
  - Realized gains/losses calculation
  - Entry and exit point analysis
  - Historical performance summary

### Portfolio Analysis
- **Holdings Breakdown:**
  - BTC Accumulation by Year (Pie Chart)
  - Average Buy Price by Year
  - Percentage of Portfolio by Entry Price

- **Cost Basis Methods:**
  - FIFO (First In, First Out)
  - LIFO (Last In, First Out)
  - Average Cost
  - Method Comparison View

- **Tax Considerations:**
  - Short-term vs. long-term holdings
  - Realized gain calculations
  - Tax year filtering

### Transaction Management
- **Transaction List:**
  - Comprehensive table of all transactions
  - Sortable columns (date, amount, type, price)
  - Type filtering (Buy, Sell, Withdrawal, Deposit)
  - Search functionality

- **Transaction Details:**
  - Full transaction information
  - Associated exchange and fees
  - Edit capability for manual entries
  - Deletion with confirmation dialog

- **CSV Export:**
  - Export transaction history to CSV
  - Customizable date ranges
  - Format options for tax software compatibility

### CSV Import System
- **File Selection and Upload:**
  - Drag & drop interface
  - File validation (size, format)
  - Support for multiple exchange formats
  - Smart format detection

- **Data Preview:**
  - Visual preview of CSV data
  - Column mapping interface
  - Validation indicators
  - Error highlighting

- **Import Process:**
  - Progress indication
  - Validation summary
  - Success confirmation
  - Error handling with retry options

- **Upload History:**
  - List of previous uploads
  - Import date and status
  - Option to delete uploads
  - Transparent transaction tracking

### Cost Basis Calculator
- **Transaction Simulation:**
  - Add hypothetical transactions
  - Model different buy/sell scenarios
  - Real-time calculation updates

- **Tax Strategy Testing:**
  - Compare different accounting methods
  - Short vs. long-term capital gains estimation
  - Scenario comparison

### Settings and Account Management
- **User Preferences:**
  - Dark/Light mode toggle
  - Default view settings
  - Default accounting method

- **Data Management:**
  - Clear all transactions
  - Delete specific uploads
  - Full account deletion option

- **Security Features:**
  - Password change
  - Email verification
  - Session management

### Mobile Experience
- **Responsive Design:**
  - Fully functional on mobile devices
  - Touch-friendly interface
  - Optimized charts and tables

- **Quick Access:**
  - Streamlined navigation
  - Essential metrics at a glance
  - Simplified data entry 